g.text: 1 Submit a proposal to New Venture Fund
2 NVF reviews and approves to confirm it aligns with values and other programs in portfolio
3 Set up an independent advisory board that governs project
5 Donations made to restricted fund for the specific project
7 Run as an independent project reporting against outcomes
8 Gain access to network services at NVF like best practices in nonprofit management, EDI, metrics, etc.
